<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>285</hymn_number>
<key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Khuazakip i rawl vialte cu, An tuan caan kha a cu cang, Tlang cung i
 le, nelrawn i zong, An za tein an hmin cang.

[C1]
   Maw, Kan Bawipa, kan in nawl ko, facang zuntu run thlah hna. A caan
   kha a luan dih hlanah, Rian rang in run thlah tuah hna.

[V2]
 Zing ah siseh, chun ah siseh, Ni a tlak dengmang zongah, Bawipa,
 hmunkip le ram kip ah, Rawltuan tu kha va fial hna.

[C2]
   Maw, Kan Bawipa, kan in nawl ko, facang zuntu run thlah hna. A caan
   kha a luan dih hlanah, Rian rang in run thlah tuah hna.

[V3]
 Maw nang, Bawipa nih, A thlahmi, Pum tuah sui facang phal cu, Na
 nunnak ni a liam tikah, Lawmhnak he naa din cang lai.

[C3]
   Maw, Kan Bawipa, kan in nawl ko, facang zuntu run thlah hna. A caan
   kha a luan dih hlanah, Rian rang in run thlah tuah hna.</lyrics>
<title>THLAICI ZUNTU AUHNAK CH285</title>
</song>